      "text": "“Oh.”",
      "next": "sisterLeans"
    },
  
    {
      "id": "sisterLeans",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Your sister catches up to you and stops in front of the building. She leans forward on her toes, trying to read the plaque.",
      "next": "ottosDiatribes"
    },

    {
      "id": "ottosDiatribes",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "erika-monsell",
      "text": "<em>“Tch</em>… Otto’s ramblings are making me blind. Truly.”",
      "next": "iThinkIsThePlace"
    },

    {
      "id": "iThinkIsThePlace",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "erika-monsell",
      "text": "“But yeah… I think this is the place.”",
      "next": "blueish"
    },

    {
      "id": "blueish",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "erika-monsell",
      "text": "“She did say it was blue… <em>ish</em>.”",
      "next": "eyesWander"
    },

    {
      "id": "cornea",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Those numbers are not getting any clearer for you. No matter how hard you squish your cornea.",
      "next": "areYouOk"
    },
  
    {
      "id": "areYouOk",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "erika-monsell",
      "text": "“Are you okay?”",
      "next": "puzzled"
    },

    {
      "id": "puzzled",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Your sister catches up to you, puzzled. She glances at the obscured plaque, then up at the third-floor windows, before her eyes return to your disoriented face.",
      "next": "blueish2"
    },

    {
      "id": "blueish2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "erika-monsell",
      "text": "“Well… she did say the place was blue… <em>ish</em>.”",
      "next": "mustBeThePlace"
    },

    {
      "id": "mustBeThePlace",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "erika-monsell",
      "text": "“This must be it.”",
      "next": "eyesWander"
    },

    {
      "id": "eyesWander",
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "She turns around; her eyes wander along the trees flanking the tranquil street, a hint of a smile on her face.",
      "next": "streetAppreciation"
    },

    {
      "id": "streetAppreciation",
      "type": "choice",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "“Peaceful, huh?”",
          "next": "yeah"
